article_id:2164,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue with the Adventurer Gala Elisanne's Ability Divine Oath III,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue that affects the adventurer Gala Elisanne after her mana spiral has been unlocked.</div><div><br></div><div>■Issue Details</div><div>When the adventurer Gala Elisanne&#39;s ability Divine Oath III activates, the effects of abilities such as Strength Doublebuff +X%, Healing Doublebuff X, and Energy Doublebuff also activate.</div><div><br></div><div>This issue will be addressed in a data update around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1621231200"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>■Goodwill Gesture</div><div>As a goodwill gesture, we will send players who unlocked Gala Elisanne&#39;s mana spiral before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1621231200"></span> the materials that they used to unlock her mana spiral nodes (excluding Gala Elisanne&#39;s Convictions and Gala Elisanne&#39;s Devotions). Any materials used to unlock up to and including the fifth mana circle will not be provided.</div><div><br></div><div>In addition, we will send 300 wyrmite to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1621231200"></span> after this issue has been addressed.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1619589600,update_time1619575732